channel.title: Comments on: the definition of culture shock

item.title: By: christio
item.dc:creator: christio
item.description: Hi Amy! I have to say, after seeing all your awesome photos of exotic places, it is a culture shock to see the burbs. How clean and sedate, and sad to say, a little mundane :-) I enjoyed reading your guys' blog...I looked forward to it every couple of days.
